{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>EVER WISHED FOR...</strong>\u00a0an\u00a0<i>Indiana Jones style\u00a0</i><strong>adventure</strong> <i>blended\u00a0with</i> an <i>old-school</i>\u00a0<strong>shooter? </strong>Light a <i>torch.\u00a0</i>Grab\u00a0your<i> shotgun. Prepare for a</i>\u00a0<strong>cursed adventure -\u00a0\u00a0</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930340/extras/ITM-CorePageBanner_main.png?t=1737319236\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>Not all that glistens in the darkness is GOLD!</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930340/extras/ITM-SteamStoreGIF_Goldpan.gif?t=1737319236\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>THE BACKSTORY</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Prepare for an atmospheric single-player adventure as you steal a map from a gang of murderous bandits that leads to cursed gold buried in the depths and darkness of an ancient mine. This old-school-inspired first person shooter features -</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engaging combat against a variety of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hand-crafted levels filled with dangerous environmental hazards to navigate and survive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gold to mine.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sticks of dynamite to throw.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Critters to squish, cursed bosses to fight and lots of weapons to shoot at the murderous gang of bandits hunting you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is a love letter to the &quot;90's child&quot; living inside all of us old-time nerds.\u00a0</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>THE GAMEPLAY</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FLUID COMBAT\u00a0</strong>will keep you on edge as you battle engaging &amp; reactive enemy AI while facing a variety of enemy types including: Bandits, critters of the mine, cursed enemies, environmental hazards, and <i>unique</i> <strong>BOSS FIGHT</strong> combat sequences!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>SMART AI</strong> ensures the murderous bandits hunting you inside the mine eventually find you and provide a unique combat experience when least expected!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930340/extras/ITM-SteamStoreGIF_BanditPunch.gif?t=1737319236\" /></p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ATMOSPHERIC ADVENTURE</strong><i>\u00a0through a single-player campaign spanning multiple chapters each containing dozens of unique hand-crafted levels.\u00a0</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930340/extras/batbar.jpg?t=1737319236\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>VOICE ACTED </strong>main character provides\u00a0<i>dynamic spoken dialog</i>\u00a0commenting on player actions and gameplay events.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">BANDITS are also<strong> voice acted -</strong>\u00a0providing a more <u><i>personal connection</i></u>\u00a0as you battle your enemies.</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>DANGEROUS ENVIROMENTAL HAZARDS</strong>\u00a0are found around every corner inside a cursed gold mine that is trying to protect its gold by actively attempting to kill you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930340/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737319236","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930340/page.bg.jpg?t=1737319236","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2930340/1bae7d289d